member.summary:
Hands off to the native MAUI Shell layer, pushing onto the navigation stack.
Because is registered as a Singleton (), Blazor's scoped DI container falls back to the root MAUI container and resolves the same instance — no extra wiring needed.
The ViewModel state (NoteTitle, Content, etc.) is NOT automatically transferred; NoteNativePage will receive a fresh Transient NoteViewModel. If you need to carry state across, persist first with SaveNoteAsync and pass the NoteId as a Shell query-parameter: await NavigationService.NavigateToAsync($"{nameof(NoteNativePage)}?noteId={id}");
